{"tid":2257741,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌撞車一問","createTime":"2020-10-25T12:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T10:45:31.000Z","uid":246054,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f61277be6d8eb0763e45e5c1d95cee1d2d48561","tid":2257741,"uid":246054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"想問如果撞到一架&lsquo;行車證&rsquo;已過期嘅車 <br />\n咁嘅情況我係咪唔洗賠錢 ？<br />\n<br />\n畀我撞到條友個行車證已經過咗期兩個月<br />\n但佢仍然喺條街行駛<br />\n然後佢一嚟就話賠幾多錢幾多錢咁<br />\n唔肯去車房報價<br />\n最後大家決定報警處理<br />\n<br />\n落口供隻狗講可能告我危險駕駛<br />\n係咪淨扣分加半年P牌同罰錢咁就完？<br />\n<br />\n利申：我有掛P牌出街"},{"pid":"df50db5c0a847b406933c49c61a24cbdbcad5176","tid":2257741,"uid":196924,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"你撞到乜都好, 只要係你錯, 都係要賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行車證過期點罰係佢嘅事, 但係唔會影響你嘅過失"},{"pid":"3cb02a3abdf2ff34e7d29c2ef19218aed3424355","tid":2257741,"uid":8500,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"咩logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3ed83838e5b127a202724463096a5be3bc3eaf","tid":2257741,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:37:58.000Z","msg":"btw 老危喎? 唔係老不?<br />\n老危你可以考過個牌啦~"},{"pid":"e7296a478f59d7156e3c477ebe97053c95ca1ff9","tid":2257741,"uid":116696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:38:38.000Z","msg":"你點撞 講黎聽下<br />\n睇下幫唔幫到你"},{"pid":"b7c6786cbad5367befbc71bb0e53038ef8c47d6c","tid":2257741,"uid":144190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人受傷先？"},{"pid":"84e704d1ddaebcf81fc4bac875d963d5d02f5c6e","tid":2257741,"uid":50872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:39:38.000Z","msg":"砍掉重練啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b90b0260e189f0ff200513981c0e96315e016b1","tid":2257741,"